Section: libs

Package: libchop-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libchop0 (= ${Source-Version})
Description: `libchop', a toolkit for distributed storage
 `libchop' is a C library that provides various tools for distributed
 storage.  Although it was primarily designed as the basis of a
 distributed cooperative backup tool, it may be applied to other
 domains such as peer-to-peer storage and version control.
 .
 This package contains the C header files.

